The '''Cutting Edge Clinic''' was a location at [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was a horrible place run by the infamous [[Cornelius Evazan/Legends|"Doctor" Cornelius]]. It had four rooms and specialized in [[Cyborg/Legends|cyborg]] operations which were seldom successfully performed. It was in this clinic that Evazan continued his research for eternal life. Evazan was aided by a [[Devaronian/Legends|Devaronian]] clerk named [[Jubel]]. Many patients had been known to disappear after making an appointment at the clinic.<ref name="GG7" />

